ai.skymind.pipelines.serving

Class PubsubConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • ai.skymind.pipelines.serving.PubsubConfig
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class PubsubConfig
extends Object
implements Serializable
    This configuration is for handling endpoints that allow asynchronous responses via a publish subscribe pattern. The basic idea is simple: You have an endpoint that receives input and a url you send a post request to with the expected output. The httpMethod allow customization but generally should be set to POST. contentType is the expected content type of the input (usually application/json) pubsubUrl is the raw url (hostname, port, routes and all) that the data should be sent to.

    Adam Gibson
